headline: 3 Brokerage Stocks Up More Than 20% in 2025 to Watch for Next Year
summary: HOOD leads a brokerage rally in 2025, followed by SCHW and IBKR, as digital trading, rising volumes and new accounts push stocks up.

headline: Looking at the Narrative for Interactive Brokers After Upgraded Targets and Crypto Focus
summary: Interactive Brokers Group’s latest narrative update comes with a slightly higher fair value estimate of about $77.33, underpinned by Street research that is increasingly confident in the broker’s technology edge, crypto roadmap, and long term growth outlook. A marginally lower discount rate and a modestly stronger revenue growth assumption signal that analysts see the company’s structural advantages outweighing near term concerns around rates, competition, and trading cyclicality. headline: Don’t Make Big Investment Moves Right Now. Stop and Think.
summary: There is nothing wrong with big banks stuffing marketing channels with 2026 predictions—it’s a fun, useful exercise—but there is little reason to do much more than read and reflect.
